reviews.text: Beautiful facility and the price was so cheap compared to other places! A flat price of 99hkd +10% services in the night and we stayed from 8h30 pm to 3h30 am! It also included 2 drinks.

The management made a mistake with pricing, and the manager interrupted us an hour into our session and shouts at us and insists we need to pay extra, although the prices were already confirmed for so long. If they had given us that price at first, we would not have come. 
Just awful hospitality and customer service. 
We were all so angry and upset for the rest of our session and our time was completely ruined by the staff.

The place was nice and we had so much fun, we paid 142 hk dollars per person(service charge included) on a friday night. The only problem was some of the english songs didn’t have lyrics on the screen.
Better food then other neway. Less people therefore less queuing time
Not too many people around, service is good.
